				<td colspan="2"><span>Well, yer first few levels lets say thru 20 you just need decent armor. Get some HP stuff. and good weapons.
<br />
Later on A TDoK for all your chants. besides this you don't need much anymore. A decent wind instrument is nice but not nesicary till later. Same with the rest of the instruments really. Clicky effects of any kind are nice as Bards stuff don't staty up long. You should have made him sooner and twinked him with a few of the fabled items that dropped. The earing and bracer from Warsilk (sp?) woods are decent items. 
<br />

<br />
Then again you been hanging around the boards for a while so you should know this. Anyways what level is yer main? Thats the main thing. Bards are adaptable get him/her what you can easily get with your main. 
<br />

