				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Twink?<a name="75555"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Apr 19 05 9:11 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Bards don't start off with all there instrument skills so you can A) buy the instrument when you get the skill for it or B) get all the instruments and keep them in the bank till to get the skill for them.
<br />
Chants are DoT songs, they are for later on, don't get any early. Bards first chant is  Tuyen's Chant of Flame at 38. Thinks I can say for twinking a bard is, HPS! if you play on soloing twink him like you would a warrior, get a good weapon and have one in bank for when he gets duel, HPs everything needs HPs on it, later on say around 40, you will need mana. I'm a 56 bard right now and everything seems to point to this format for gear, there is a 5 item order I use when looking to up-grade armor.
<br />
Item 1 : Hps = Hps or sta on the item
<br />
Item 2 : mana = mana or int on the item
<br />
Item 3 : MR = magic resist on the item
<br />
Item 4 : cha = Cha on the item
<br />
Item 5 : Everthing else
<br />
</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
