				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Twink?<a name="75564"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Apr 19 05 2:05 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>If you are going to straight PL the bard to the 40 range, then gear him up as a level 40, where things that will be important are drum mods, HP, mana. The things bards lack in the 40's are mana, FT, and defense, so agi will be nice.
<br />

<br />
If you are going to twink him to solo the whole time or group and just want good gear for him, look at haste, HP, sta, a decent string mod for hp regen, and I recommend agi/ac. Cha is useless pretty much lower level, as is int. Dex is limited in its usefullness but shouldn't be ignored completely. Bards are aggro magnets low level, keep that in mind. A 4 twist of songs can grab aggro from an inexperienced tank, so have the gear that will help you tank and take the abuse. Just my 2cp, ymmv.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
